{"tid":877665,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"出game要政府批准　但最後審批渠道已關　中國遊戲業出現地下市場","createTime":"2018-10-26T13:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T02:44:09.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"764e060766b66a8925937ead758a927d31d2a910","tid":877665,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/finance/5bd00531e60383df34ac8173\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ffinance%2F5bd00531e60383df34ac8173&d=8qb7ErW17zENeG%2Bm5Z6UoxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=aff030d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/finance/5bd00531e60383df34ac8173</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/Mckz35\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FMckz35&h=c5e21ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有報道指，內地已關閉網絡遊戲審批的「綠色通道」。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》引述消息指，內地已完成停止遊戲審批的「綠色通道」。此通道最早在八月已經實施，容許新遊戲毋須審批，臨時推出一個月。<br />\n<br />\n據報業界因應暫停審批新遊戲，尋找其他盈利來源，包括持續更新現有遊戲，例如創造新場景或武器、延長遊戲生命周期，甚至出現地下市場買賣遊戲發行權，但價格由以往每隻最多約50萬元人民幣，降至近期最低20萬元人民幣。"},{"pid":"f9b585b02846e53cd045f2981bcccdb5d29ec3ae","tid":877665,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T00:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e082043058acb1a82db49811ccc6f23de49a5449","tid":877665,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"機都唔比打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8509820e0f529a1b2759cde1e3c48ee4217a572d","tid":877665,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"會否係個商機？"},{"pid":"049948954da2778ec8cead94edc3940397063db2","tid":877665,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"漫畫都要審<br />\n唔係game一樣<br />\n聽聞好多漫畫都被沒收"},{"pid":"e07f5ff7e59a63f0a522a6ebb56e03ed91337e6f","tid":877665,"uid":21